cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper is about a reinforcement learning approach, specifically a modification to the popular Proximal Policy Optimization (PPO) algorithm. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which includes subcategories related to reinforcement learning. The paper also draws inspiration from an evolutionary optimization method, which suggests a possible fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The application of the algorithm to Roboschool continuous control benchmarks suggests a fit with cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
